00:01:44.580 --> 00:01:47.260
(Rain Manor)

00:01:50.480 --> 00:01:51.680
Your wound isn't a huge issue.

00:01:51.977 --> 00:01:54.280
You'll be fine after
getting a suture in the hospital.

00:01:54.511 --> 00:01:56.280
Thank you.
We're lucky that you're around.

00:01:56.288 --> 00:01:57.040
Thank you so much.

00:01:57.200 --> 00:01:57.920
Don't mention it.

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:02.519
Everyone, we're truly sorry

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:04.480
that something upsetting had happened.

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:06.480
Please don't hold it against us.

00:02:14.199 --> 00:02:15.599
The envelope beside you all

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:17.560
is the reward Master
had prepared for you all.

00:02:17.919 --> 00:02:19.400
According to him,

00:02:19.400 --> 00:02:21.039
winning or losing doesn't matter.

00:02:21.044 --> 00:02:22.555
Participation is the most important.

00:02:25.180 --> 00:02:27.340
(Mr. Pan Jingting,
10,000 silver dollars)

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:29.319
Yu.

00:02:30.240 --> 00:02:32.000
I can't accept this reward.

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:32.800
Elder Yu,

00:02:33.288 --> 00:02:34.840
we can't accept the reward either.

00:02:35.199 --> 00:02:36.000
That's right.

00:02:36.266 --> 00:02:37.400
We attended the banquet

00:02:37.639 --> 00:02:39.120
in order to visit you

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:41.000
and check how you were doing.

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:42.280
As your junior,

00:02:42.319 --> 00:02:43.749
having been three years away from you

00:02:43.750 --> 00:02:45.488
is already considered
irresponsible of us.

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:47.199
We mustn't accept your rewards now.

00:02:48.520 --> 00:02:49.840
Are you guys

00:02:50.319 --> 00:02:51.960
belittling me?

00:02:55.560 --> 00:02:56.240
Godfather,

00:02:57.080 --> 00:02:58.280
I came here initially

00:02:58.280 --> 00:02:59.759
to visit both you

00:02:59.759 --> 00:03:01.199
and Xiuyun.

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:03.800
Xiuyun's death anniversary is nearing.

00:03:04.240 --> 00:03:06.639
Why don't I arrange a car
for us to visit her together?

00:03:06.919 --> 00:03:08.280
I should do the arrangement.

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:09.319
We'll join as well.

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:10.520
All of us will be going.

00:03:13.159 --> 00:03:14.360
It seems you all

00:03:16.719 --> 00:03:17.759
still remember Xiuyun.

00:03:18.879 --> 00:03:21.000
I'm truly moved.

00:03:21.919 --> 00:03:23.960
I'm content now.

00:03:24.919 --> 00:03:25.800
All right.

00:03:26.319 --> 00:03:27.199
By then,

00:03:28.439 --> 00:03:29.599
let us

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:31.319
visit her grave together.

00:03:34.479 --> 00:03:36.000
I've indeed blamed you guys

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:40.599
for Xiuyun's death before.

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:44.680
I've also blamed myself for it.

00:03:45.319 --> 00:03:46.199
However,

00:03:47.039 --> 00:03:48.879
it's pointless to do so.

00:03:51.560 --> 00:03:52.800
I pride myself

00:03:53.177 --> 00:03:54.910
on having some knowledge about antiques

00:03:55.520 --> 00:03:57.560
and spending
my entire life studying them.

00:03:58.360 --> 00:04:01.240
But I lack the broad-mindedness
of our predecessors.

00:04:02.759 --> 00:04:05.000
I just can't bring myself to be humble.

00:04:05.639 --> 00:04:06.800
I'm ashamed of myself.

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.560
Those of us who are still alive

00:04:10.759 --> 00:04:12.759
should live on.

00:04:13.599 --> 00:04:16.040
It's not just for our sake.

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:18.759
It also represents Xiuyun's hope.

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:24.000
I suppose

00:04:25.399 --> 00:04:27.079
my actions

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:28.879
had intimidated you all last night.

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:30.759
I...

00:04:30.959 --> 00:04:31.879
Here,

00:04:32.639 --> 00:04:34.199
I would like to

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:39.399
apologize to you all sincerely.

00:04:40.079 --> 00:04:40.920
I'm truly sorry.

00:04:45.199 --> 00:04:46.800
I feel exhausted.

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:49.160
Everyone,

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:51.279
if you have something else to do,

00:04:52.040 --> 00:04:54.079
please proceed on your own.

00:04:54.399 --> 00:04:57.120
Please pardon me
for not being able to see you off.

00:05:06.519 --> 00:05:08.000
For this match,

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:10.720
you're the winner.

00:05:11.560 --> 00:05:13.279
I will keep my promise.

00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:14.759
The Liubo Chess set

00:05:16.079 --> 00:05:17.079
is yours now.

00:05:18.480 --> 00:05:19.560
Thank you, Elder Yu.

00:05:31.780 --> 00:05:36.199
(Rain Manor)

00:05:36.199 --> 00:05:37.480
Here, slowly.

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:41.629
From tomorrow onward,

00:05:41.630 --> 00:05:44.620
I'll devote my effort to training those
who will participate in the contest.

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:47.319
As for the martial arts center,
I'll leave it to you entirely.

00:05:50.120 --> 00:05:50.759
Brother,

00:05:51.959 --> 00:05:53.519
I'm afraid I can't handle it myself.

00:05:54.319 --> 00:05:56.160
Before this, I was training our students

00:05:56.266 --> 00:05:58.040
and managing our business
at the same time.

00:05:58.333 --> 00:06:00.311
I was spread too thin
to manage everything.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:03.480
You were good at studying
from a young age.

00:06:03.839 --> 00:06:05.120
You're smarter than me.

00:06:05.639 --> 00:06:06.879
I should've left you in charge

00:06:06.879 --> 00:06:08.800
of our business long ago.

00:06:09.879 --> 00:06:10.439
Chi,

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:13.319
I'll be depending on you in the future.

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:15.839
Brother...

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:18.480
Let's go.

00:06:18.959 --> 00:06:19.759
Come.

00:06:21.199 --> 00:06:22.000
Slowly.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:23.844
(Rain Manor)

00:06:26.199 --> 00:06:27.000
Slowly.

00:06:38.839 --> 00:06:39.439
Let's go.

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:40.399
Let's go.

00:06:40.444 --> 00:06:41.830
For your performance next Tuesday,

00:06:42.133 --> 00:06:43.577
I'll head there together with you.

00:06:47.160 --> 00:06:48.000
In the next few days,

00:06:48.044 --> 00:06:50.080
I'll hold a discussion
with the Chamber of Commerce.

00:06:50.133 --> 00:06:52.260
I'll tell them about
the machines you intend to buy.

00:06:52.720 --> 00:06:53.319
Father...

00:06:53.879 --> 00:06:55.160
It's just a discussion.

00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:56.720
It might not necessarily work out.

00:07:01.839 --> 00:07:03.519
I'll try my best to persuade them.

00:07:05.879 --> 00:07:06.360
Thank you.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:07.120
Thank you, Father.

00:07:22.759 --> 00:07:24.079
We need to walk quite a distance.

00:07:24.399 --> 00:07:25.319
Can you do it?

00:07:53.460 --> 00:07:56.500
(Rain Manor)

00:07:58.100 --> 00:08:01.740
(One Month Later)

00:08:06.860 --> 00:08:12.340
(Grave of Yu Xiuyun)

00:08:33.639 --> 00:08:34.840
Everyone, thank you

00:08:35.879 --> 00:08:38.080
for visiting Xiuyun
together with me today.

00:08:38.840 --> 00:08:39.639
Thank you.

00:08:44.879 --> 00:08:45.679
Yu,

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:47.519
your car isn't here.

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:50.000
Let me send you back.

00:08:50.480 --> 00:08:51.240
No need for that.

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:54.240
The car Ning had arranged for
is waiting for me down the hill.

00:08:54.960 --> 00:08:55.759
Thank you so much.

00:09:12.039 --> 00:09:12.840
Master?

00:09:15.919 --> 00:09:16.559
Master.

00:09:16.639 --> 00:09:17.879
I'm Cao A'ning.

00:09:18.679 --> 00:09:19.559
I'm truly sorry

00:09:19.559 --> 00:09:20.600
that I'm only here now.

00:09:20.879 --> 00:09:22.919
You're Cao A'ning?

00:09:23.022 --> 00:09:23.630
That's right.

00:09:23.960 --> 00:09:25.480
Butler Li introduced me to you.

00:09:25.519 --> 00:09:26.840
Butler Li is my uncle.

00:09:27.759 --> 00:09:29.320
I'm truly sorry about this.

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:32.399
My ID card was stolen
on my way to your manor.

00:09:32.399 --> 00:09:34.720
That's why my trip was delayed.

00:09:36.759 --> 00:09:38.919
I've already notified my uncle
at the first time.

00:09:38.933 --> 00:09:40.888
I'll definitely
pay more attention next time.

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:41.720
If so,

00:09:41.879 --> 00:09:44.720
the previous Miss Ning...

00:09:45.200 --> 00:09:46.360
Who was she?

00:10:11.480 --> 00:10:12.000
Look.

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:13.600
This bow alone has several variations.

00:10:13.679 --> 00:10:14.919
Where did we get these?

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:17.320
Mr. Chu went to great pains
to find them for us.

00:10:17.355 --> 00:10:19.622
And look at how beautiful
this feathered shuttlecock is.

00:10:21.679 --> 00:10:22.879
It's been so long

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:24.759
since Luoxia Manor was this lively.

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:25.840
But

00:10:25.840 --> 00:10:28.279
we still don't know which guest
Market Lord is expecting.

00:10:29.000 --> 00:10:29.799
Let's hurry.

00:10:37.320 --> 00:10:38.120
Chu Qiu,

00:10:39.320 --> 00:10:41.279
how long have we waited?

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:50.120
There's no concept of time
in Tianguang Market.

00:10:50.519 --> 00:10:52.480
None of us knew how long we'd waited.

00:10:54.360 --> 00:10:55.279
Say,

00:10:55.559 --> 00:10:58.440
when Butler Su and Bizhi arrive later,

00:10:58.559 --> 00:11:01.360
how should I scold them
to make it seem more justified?

00:11:04.960 --> 00:11:05.679
Market Lord,

00:11:05.930 --> 00:11:07.479
the rice dumplings stick to your teeth.

00:11:07.480 --> 00:11:09.390
It'll cause indigestion
if you consume too much of it.

00:11:09.390 --> 00:11:10.488
You should stop eating it.

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:12.159
What do you know?

00:11:12.879 --> 00:11:15.440
I just want to have
a proper celebration.

00:11:15.688 --> 00:11:17.800
It doesn't matter
even if it's the Cold Food Festival.

00:11:18.559 --> 00:11:19.240
But in the end,

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:20.559
someone stood me up.

00:11:22.639 --> 00:11:23.720
This is ridiculous!

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:25.759
How dare they stand me up?

00:11:28.466 --> 00:11:30.840
Market Lord, since you want
to have a proper celebration,

00:11:31.320 --> 00:11:32.399
you should follow me.

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:35.000
Where are we going?

00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:36.360
Just follow me.

00:11:40.279 --> 00:11:41.480
Where are we going?

00:11:41.639 --> 00:11:42.799
Don't open your eyes first.

00:11:43.240 --> 00:11:44.080
Mind your steps.

00:11:48.279 --> 00:11:49.360
Mind your steps.

00:11:53.840 --> 00:11:54.919
Are we there yet?

00:11:55.320 --> 00:11:56.039
We'll arrive soon.

00:11:57.639 --> 00:11:58.159
Here we are.

00:11:58.480 --> 00:11:59.759
May I open my eyes now?

00:11:59.759 --> 00:12:00.200
You may.

00:12:02.720 --> 00:12:04.360
Why did you bring me here?

00:12:04.466 --> 00:12:05.790
What's so special about this?

00:12:05.799 --> 00:12:07.360
Isn't this the Forgetting Tree?

00:12:11.679 --> 00:12:12.759
A swing?

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:17.080
Did you make this for me?

00:12:19.759 --> 00:12:23.120
Did you actually commit it to heart
when I said I had fun on a swing

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:24.666
together with my parents in my dream?

00:12:25.511 --> 00:12:27.933
People do play with swings
during Cold Food Festival as well.

00:12:28.519 --> 00:12:29.320
You're the best.

00:12:34.240 --> 00:12:34.879
Come here.

00:12:36.440 --> 00:12:37.320
Give me a push.

00:12:42.320 --> 00:12:42.960
Go ahead.

00:12:46.919 --> 00:12:47.720
Higher.

00:12:49.799 --> 00:12:50.840
Say,

00:12:51.159 --> 00:12:52.840
why didn't they come?

00:12:53.399 --> 00:12:54.840
Perhaps something cropped up.

00:12:55.399 --> 00:12:56.480
What did you say?

00:12:57.360 --> 00:12:58.440
Perhaps

00:12:58.440 --> 00:12:59.679
something cropped up.

00:13:00.759 --> 00:13:01.559
Wrong.

00:13:02.159 --> 00:13:03.440
Let me tell you why.

00:13:03.759 --> 00:13:04.639
It's because

00:13:04.759 --> 00:13:06.759
Bizhi only has one item left

00:13:06.799 --> 00:13:09.720
that he needs to collect.

00:13:27.440 --> 00:13:29.000
Doctor!

00:13:31.360 --> 00:13:32.240
Follow me!

00:13:32.519 --> 00:13:33.480
Please save him!

00:13:33.480 --> 00:13:34.279
Come with me.

00:13:36.679 --> 00:13:37.639
Hurry!

00:13:43.639 --> 00:13:44.639
(In this era,)

00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:47.399
(although humans remain helpless)

00:13:47.519 --> 00:13:48.799
(against illness and death,)

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:50.679
(at least)

00:13:50.919 --> 00:13:53.320
(everyone is trying their best to live.)

00:13:54.080 --> 00:13:54.840
(Where life goes,)

00:13:55.240 --> 00:13:56.200
(death follows.)

00:13:56.639 --> 00:13:57.639
(If we meet someone,)

00:13:58.279 --> 00:13:59.960
(that means we'll part ways)

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:01.240
(eventually.)

00:14:02.799 --> 00:14:04.519
(Is it time for me to leave?)

00:14:05.559 --> 00:14:07.440
(But I'm not ready yet.)

00:14:10.559 --> 00:14:11.559
Don't move.

00:14:12.559 --> 00:14:13.399
Don't move.

00:14:14.519 --> 00:14:15.120
Don't move!

00:14:19.759 --> 00:14:20.240
All done.

00:14:20.240 --> 00:14:21.000
Get up.

00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:23.022
Your wound is healing quite nicely.

00:14:23.088 --> 00:14:24.720
Although the stitches have been removed,

00:14:24.799 --> 00:14:27.159
keep the wound dry
for the next couple of days.

00:14:27.288 --> 00:14:28.670
Don't pull on it too hard either.

00:14:28.879 --> 00:14:30.320
Avoid spicy food.

00:14:30.480 --> 00:14:31.399
I know that.

00:14:31.400 --> 00:14:32.369
I was one of your peers.

00:14:32.370 --> 00:14:34.320
I used to be in charge
of removing stitches myself.

00:14:34.320 --> 00:14:35.480
You possess excellent skills.

00:14:35.480 --> 00:14:36.860
Which hospital did you work at before?

00:14:36.866 --> 00:14:37.600
Chongle Hospital.

00:14:37.600 --> 00:14:38.960
I've never heard of that name before.

00:14:38.960 --> 00:14:40.440
It's a pet hospital after all.

00:14:40.519 --> 00:14:41.000
See you.

00:14:48.244 --> 00:14:49.000
Boss!

00:14:50.955 --> 00:14:51.800
How are you?

00:14:51.866 --> 00:14:52.670
I've fully recovered.

00:14:54.340 --> 00:14:56.622
It's a shame that they didn't
get rid of your foolishness.

00:14:56.960 --> 00:14:57.600
Let's go.

00:14:58.399 --> 00:14:59.639
But, Boss, you see,

00:14:59.666 --> 00:15:02.120
it's more convenient for us
after the stitches are removed,

00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:02.977
unlike dogs and cats.

00:15:03.000 --> 00:15:05.080
They love to lick their wound
after the stitches have been removed.

00:15:05.080 --> 00:15:06.720
And, if you give them
an Elizabeth collar,

00:15:06.720 --> 00:15:07.840
they'll turn into a trumpet.

00:15:08.039 --> 00:15:09.440
Do you want one, then?

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:11.444
If you give me one,
I'll give you one in return.

00:15:14.840 --> 00:15:16.000
Another year has passed.

00:15:16.159 --> 00:15:17.120
What do you mean?

00:15:17.444 --> 00:15:19.377
It's been a year since the day we met.

00:15:19.799 --> 00:15:21.720
That night, you were super drunk.

00:15:21.720 --> 00:15:23.399
If I didn't send you home back then...

00:15:23.519 --> 00:15:25.240
Don't bring it up again.

00:15:26.559 --> 00:15:27.200
Sure.

00:15:27.444 --> 00:15:29.222
But you have to buy me some ice cream.

00:15:30.120 --> 00:15:31.919
Ice cream is meant for kids, you know?

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:33.919
Who said so?

00:15:34.159 --> 00:15:35.600
Both adults and kids love it.

00:15:35.840 --> 00:15:37.720
I loved ice cream when I was a kid.

00:15:38.279 --> 00:15:40.799
But my grandma
only sold popsicles in her store.

00:15:41.240 --> 00:15:42.639
Back then, ice cream was expensive.

00:15:42.977 --> 00:15:44.480
Grandma would only buy it for me

00:15:44.519 --> 00:15:45.919
when I did great.

00:15:47.000 --> 00:15:48.279
Now that I'm all grown up,

00:15:48.720 --> 00:15:50.559
whenever I want to buy ice cream,

00:15:50.840 --> 00:15:51.639
I'll ponder over it

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:54.200
and wonder

00:15:54.679 --> 00:15:56.159
if I did well

00:15:56.559 --> 00:15:58.360
and if I deserved the ice cream.

00:16:00.111 --> 00:16:02.000
After that,
I won't feel like eating it anymore.

00:16:04.480 --> 00:16:06.679
Now, you can buy
all the ice cream you want.

00:16:07.600 --> 00:16:08.200
Let's go.

00:16:08.266 --> 00:16:09.270
I'll buy you ice cream.

00:16:09.759 --> 00:16:10.480
Sure.

00:16:10.879 --> 00:16:12.279
I want honeydew-flavored ice cream.

00:16:14.480 --> 00:16:15.000
Miss,

00:16:15.039 --> 00:16:16.759
I want honeydew-flavored ice cream.

00:16:16.759 --> 00:16:17.440
Sure.

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:18.480
Only one?

00:16:18.480 --> 00:16:19.169
Yeah, only one.

00:16:19.170 --> 00:16:20.540
He wants a strawberry-flavored one.

00:16:20.559 --> 00:16:21.919
I want vanilla.

00:16:22.559 --> 00:16:25.120
One honeydew and one vanilla, right?

00:16:25.511 --> 00:16:26.510
Please give me a moment.

00:16:29.480 --> 00:16:30.120
How much?

00:16:30.120 --> 00:16:31.799
15 yuan for one.
Just leave it there.

00:16:34.279 --> 00:16:37.480
Today's the 15th of March 2025.

00:16:37.519 --> 00:16:39.399
My stitches have been removed!

00:16:39.480 --> 00:16:40.960
The weather today is scorching.

00:16:40.960 --> 00:16:42.120
But we're super lucky.

00:16:42.120 --> 00:16:43.960
We bumped into an ice cream truck.

00:16:44.039 --> 00:16:46.879
And, Bizhi is buying me
an ice cream, too.

00:16:48.039 --> 00:16:48.879
Thank you, Boss!

00:16:50.519 --> 00:16:51.440
Here's your ice cream.

00:16:51.759 --> 00:16:52.480
Thanks.

00:16:52.799 --> 00:16:53.840
Speaking of which,

00:16:54.519 --> 00:16:56.399
Bizhi is the third person

00:16:56.510 --> 00:16:58.500
who actually bought me ice cream
after my grandma.

