00:31:13.039 --> 00:31:15.440
Scholar Zhao, I don't know
why you're trying to hide it.

00:31:15.759 --> 00:31:17.480
But I'm earnest
in procuring the painting.

00:31:18.000 --> 00:31:20.550
The price can be negotiated
as long as you're willing to sell it.

00:31:20.550 --> 00:31:22.380
I'll provide you
with all the liquor you want.

00:31:22.390 --> 00:31:24.660
You said this Autumn Twilight Painting
was worth 500 wen.

00:31:24.880 --> 00:31:25.799
I'll be taking it.

00:31:26.079 --> 00:31:26.839
Hey.

00:31:27.555 --> 00:31:28.790
Are you actually buying it?

00:31:37.319 --> 00:31:38.039
Farewell.

00:31:44.440 --> 00:31:45.240
Let's go.

00:32:03.920 --> 00:32:05.359
I have enough money for alcohol now.

00:32:08.119 --> 00:32:09.480
How could he do this?

00:32:09.720 --> 00:32:10.759
He forced a deal,

00:32:10.844 --> 00:32:12.622
and he even
deceived people with imitations.

00:32:12.799 --> 00:32:13.519
But,

00:32:13.920 --> 00:32:16.599
is the Autumn Twilight Painting
a famous painting?

00:32:16.600 --> 00:32:18.355
It became very famous
in later generations.

00:32:18.400 --> 00:32:19.799
But it's not popular yet right now.

00:32:20.288 --> 00:32:22.000
Over a century ago,
Gu Zhiqian was merely

00:32:22.000 --> 00:32:24.599
an unappreciated, down-and-out scholar.

00:32:24.890 --> 00:32:26.720
He repeatedly took
the imperial examinations

00:32:26.720 --> 00:32:27.880
but failed every time.

00:32:27.880 --> 00:32:29.288
In the end, he died of depression.

00:32:30.559 --> 00:32:32.440
Although his paintings
are masterfully painted,

00:32:32.511 --> 00:32:33.720
and possess a distinct style,

00:32:33.759 --> 00:32:35.920
people in this era only wish

00:32:35.960 --> 00:32:37.960
to pass the imperial exam
and strike it rich.

00:32:38.480 --> 00:32:40.440
His paintings are
considered inauspicious.

00:32:40.880 --> 00:32:43.519
So, it's not enough
for the paintings to be of high caliber.

00:32:43.622 --> 00:32:45.030
They have to be auspicious as well?

00:32:45.519 --> 00:32:48.880
If you're bent on becoming
the top scholar and an official,

00:32:49.288 --> 00:32:51.720
will you collect the paintings
of an unfortunate soul?

00:32:53.400 --> 00:32:54.559
If so, why did Zhao Wanli

00:32:54.559 --> 00:32:56.319
copy so many of the same paintings?

00:32:56.640 --> 00:32:58.119
Is he not afraid of bad luck?

00:33:03.839 --> 00:33:05.240
Let's ask him that question.

00:33:09.440 --> 00:33:10.039
Sir.

00:33:10.039 --> 00:33:11.160
I'm not selling them.

00:33:23.400 --> 00:33:25.240
It's not even closing time yet.

00:33:25.559 --> 00:33:26.680
Where is he going?

00:33:31.300 --> 00:33:32.720
(3,000 Drunken Tavern)

00:33:32.720 --> 00:33:34.160
Scholar Zhao is here.

00:33:34.466 --> 00:33:36.160
You did great
at maintaining the flowers.

00:33:36.200 --> 00:33:37.079
Scholar Zhao.

00:33:38.920 --> 00:33:39.680
You're here again.

00:33:52.640 --> 00:33:53.519
Enjoy yourself.

00:33:54.039 --> 00:33:55.000
Madam Ran.

00:33:55.480 --> 00:33:56.680
How are you doing today?

00:33:57.400 --> 00:33:58.359
What are you doing here?

00:33:58.430 --> 00:33:59.480
Didn't I tell you already?

00:33:59.480 --> 00:34:01.820
Don't come back unless you have
enough to pay off your tab.

00:34:01.839 --> 00:34:03.440
Madam Ran, I beg to differ.

00:34:04.359 --> 00:34:06.440
We've known each other
for so many years.

00:34:06.720 --> 00:34:08.280
How could I take advantage of you?

00:34:08.280 --> 00:34:09.311
Come on.

00:34:10.119 --> 00:34:10.960
Take a look.

00:34:12.800 --> 00:34:13.719
Just look.

00:34:13.933 --> 00:34:16.440
(Ran Zhou'er, Shopkeeper
of 3,000 Drunken Tavern)

00:34:16.440 --> 00:34:18.280
You actually sold
some paintings today, huh?

00:34:18.280 --> 00:34:19.360
Of course.

00:34:24.280 --> 00:34:25.519
Give me a large vat.

00:34:32.039 --> 00:34:33.920
Madam Ran, thank you for the wine.

00:34:48.044 --> 00:34:49.866
Nothing is more elegant
than poetry and books.

00:34:50.288 --> 00:34:52.710
Nothing is more beautiful
than what's inside this pot.

00:34:54.044 --> 00:34:55.400
And, nothing is more fragrant

00:34:55.760 --> 00:34:57.679
than Madam Ran's braised pork head.

00:34:57.755 --> 00:34:59.377
Have something to eat first

00:34:59.400 --> 00:35:01.320
so that you won't puke
and dirty my shop again.

00:35:01.320 --> 00:35:03.159
Madam Ran, I'll learn from my lesson.

00:35:03.320 --> 00:35:04.159
You're right.

00:35:04.679 --> 00:35:06.239
You and your silver tongue.

00:35:06.866 --> 00:35:08.030
Let's make a promise today.

00:35:08.030 --> 00:35:09.190
At most, you'll have one vat.

00:35:09.840 --> 00:35:10.519
Understood.

00:35:10.719 --> 00:35:11.480
Understood.

00:35:13.244 --> 00:35:14.920
(3,000 Drunken Tavern)

00:35:14.920 --> 00:35:16.280
The braised pork head is delicious.

00:35:16.559 --> 00:35:17.639
Here, try this.

00:35:17.800 --> 00:35:19.400
Life is but a grand dream,

00:35:19.519 --> 00:35:21.159
why trouble oneself?

00:35:21.755 --> 00:35:23.688
Better to spend the days
in drunken ease,

00:35:24.199 --> 00:35:25.960
finding comfort
whether sitting or standing.

00:35:34.280 --> 00:35:35.039
Madam Ran,

00:35:35.133 --> 00:35:35.840
give me the tab.

00:35:36.079 --> 00:35:36.840
Coming.

00:35:41.559 --> 00:35:42.360
20 wen.

00:35:45.199 --> 00:35:45.960
Madam Ran...

00:35:46.200 --> 00:35:47.222
What are you doing?

00:35:47.320 --> 00:35:48.760
Look at how fierce you look.

00:35:48.880 --> 00:35:50.159
It's no wonder you're unmarried

00:35:50.159 --> 00:35:51.480
even at this age.

00:35:51.519 --> 00:35:52.760
That's none of your business.

00:35:54.119 --> 00:35:55.960
Today, it's my business.

00:35:56.555 --> 00:35:57.630
What are you guys up to?

00:35:57.639 --> 00:35:58.639
What do you think?

00:35:58.639 --> 00:36:00.100
This is a warning! Stay away from me!

00:36:00.119 --> 00:36:00.920
Such audacity!

00:36:04.679 --> 00:36:06.159
How dare you two do such a thing?

00:36:06.679 --> 00:36:08.519
How dare you bully Madam Ran

00:36:08.519 --> 00:36:09.960
in front of me?

00:36:10.066 --> 00:36:11.110
Do you have a death wish?

00:36:11.119 --> 00:36:11.760
Go away!

00:36:11.760 --> 00:36:13.080
Where did this old fool come from?

00:36:13.090 --> 00:36:14.199
Look at how drunk he is.

00:36:14.199 --> 00:36:15.519
Can he save a damsel in distress?

00:36:15.519 --> 00:36:16.360
Who are you calling an old fool?

00:36:16.360 --> 00:36:17.199
You.

00:36:17.880 --> 00:36:18.599
I'll spit on you!

00:36:18.760 --> 00:36:19.719
What the heck?

00:36:19.866 --> 00:36:21.000
What are you trying to do?

00:36:26.955 --> 00:36:28.200
That felt great.

00:36:28.244 --> 00:36:30.000
You dirtied my garment!
You can't afford it!

00:36:30.039 --> 00:36:30.800
Old fool!

00:36:30.800 --> 00:36:32.200
You're itching for a beating, huh?

00:36:32.288 --> 00:36:33.840
Do you know how much my garment costs?

00:36:34.400 --> 00:36:35.400
Let him go!

00:36:36.639 --> 00:36:38.400
How dare you cause trouble in my tavern?

00:36:38.480 --> 00:36:38.960
Scram!

00:36:39.622 --> 00:36:40.280
Calm down!

00:36:40.355 --> 00:36:40.777
Calm down!

00:36:41.155 --> 00:36:43.155
Don't think that you can
bully girls all you want!

00:36:43.360 --> 00:36:44.480
You perverted fools.

00:36:47.039 --> 00:36:48.840
Madam Ran, you're the best.

00:36:53.880 --> 00:36:54.679
Wake up.

00:36:55.000 --> 00:36:55.920
Wake up.

00:36:56.000 --> 00:36:57.844
Didn't we say that
you'd only drink one vat?

00:36:57.960 --> 00:36:59.079
You drank so much.

00:36:59.133 --> 00:37:00.710
That money you gave me isn't enough.

00:37:01.119 --> 00:37:02.599
I'll pay his tab.

00:37:04.844 --> 00:37:06.030
You guys will pay for him?

00:37:06.360 --> 00:37:07.039
Yeah.

00:37:07.480 --> 00:37:10.360
We came to this city just so
we could buy a painting from him.

00:37:10.480 --> 00:37:12.000
Since you're close to him,

00:37:12.159 --> 00:37:14.039
can you tell us his address?

00:37:14.280 --> 00:37:15.719
We can send him back

00:37:15.733 --> 00:37:16.880
as a sign of our sincerity.

00:37:17.360 --> 00:37:18.639
Send him back?

00:37:19.719 --> 00:37:20.800
His address?

00:37:21.039 --> 00:37:21.880
It's very far away.

00:37:23.639 --> 00:37:24.599
Are we there yet?

00:37:30.559 --> 00:37:31.559
Where is it?

00:37:33.920 --> 00:37:35.000
I think this is the place.

00:37:37.239 --> 00:37:39.000
I'm not drunk.

00:37:41.199 --> 00:37:42.400
Hold him. I'll get the door.

00:37:42.400 --> 00:37:42.880
Okay.

00:37:45.360 --> 00:37:45.840
Here.

00:37:46.320 --> 00:37:47.079
Slowly.

00:37:47.599 --> 00:37:48.639
I'm not drunk.

00:37:54.599 --> 00:37:55.440
Here.

00:37:56.920 --> 00:37:57.599
Slowly.

00:38:03.320 --> 00:38:04.119
Light the candle.

00:38:18.079 --> 00:38:18.920
What are you doing?

00:38:18.930 --> 00:38:20.555
I'm looking for
the Autumn Twilight Painting.

00:38:20.559 --> 00:38:21.679
This is wrong. Give it to me.

00:38:22.888 --> 00:38:24.630
Didn't you tell me to light the candle

00:38:25.079 --> 00:38:26.599
so that we could look for the painting?

00:38:27.159 --> 00:38:28.440
I told you to light the candle

00:38:28.519 --> 00:38:30.760
to leave him with
a ray of light in the darkness.

00:38:31.719 --> 00:38:33.400
You're so kind.

00:38:33.800 --> 00:38:34.760
Just look at him.

00:38:34.760 --> 00:38:35.710
So many paintings here.

00:38:35.720 --> 00:38:36.679
He's a painting fanatic.

00:38:36.679 --> 00:38:37.920
If so, these are likely to be...

00:38:37.920 --> 00:38:38.920
This might be it...

00:38:39.000 --> 00:38:39.559
Su Beilu,

00:38:39.639 --> 00:38:40.280
give it to me.

00:38:40.280 --> 00:38:41.880
I'm not here to take his painting.

00:38:41.880 --> 00:38:43.079
I just want to take a look.

00:38:43.079 --> 00:38:44.400
Hurry and put it down!

00:38:44.400 --> 00:38:45.109
Don't take it!

00:38:45.110 --> 00:38:46.288
I just want to take a look!

00:38:50.760 --> 00:38:52.880
So, you two wanted
to steal my painting, huh?

00:38:56.320 --> 00:38:58.422
Scholar Zhao, it's not what you think.

00:38:58.444 --> 00:38:59.670
Please listen to me.

00:38:59.679 --> 00:39:00.519
Stop denying it!

00:39:01.199 --> 00:39:03.280
You two may look like decent people,

00:39:03.679 --> 00:39:05.679
but you actually tried
to steal my paintings!

00:39:05.679 --> 00:39:07.000
So what if I looked at your paintings?

00:39:07.000 --> 00:39:08.180
You deceived us this morning!

00:39:08.190 --> 00:39:08.840
Shut up!

00:39:08.840 --> 00:39:10.880
Stealing one's paintings is
like murdering one's parents!

00:39:10.880 --> 00:39:11.440
It's a misunderstanding.

00:39:11.440 --> 00:39:12.599
We sent you home out of kind intentions!

00:39:12.599 --> 00:39:13.400
Shut up!

00:39:13.400 --> 00:39:14.622
This is a misunderstanding!

00:39:14.622 --> 00:39:15.400
What are you doing?

00:39:15.400 --> 00:39:16.559
Can you please calm down?

00:39:17.199 --> 00:39:18.239
This is a misunderstanding!

00:39:18.239 --> 00:39:19.119
Please calm down!

00:39:20.039 --> 00:39:20.760
Scholar Zhao!

00:39:20.760 --> 00:39:21.159
Scram!

00:39:22.840 --> 00:39:24.719
That stupid fool.

00:39:25.360 --> 00:39:26.920
He thinks he can steal my paintings.

00:39:27.559 --> 00:39:29.480
I thought he was an alcoholic.

00:39:30.244 --> 00:39:31.590
It turns out that he's a lunatic.

00:39:31.644 --> 00:39:32.550
That stupid fool...

00:39:32.559 --> 00:39:34.719
Why is he this terrifying when drunk?

00:39:34.719 --> 00:39:36.400
We don't do that when we get drunk.

00:39:36.599 --> 00:39:38.599
He lets loose when he gets drunk!

00:39:38.666 --> 00:39:39.920
Let's return to Yashe for now.

00:39:39.920 --> 00:39:40.760
We shouldn't.

00:39:41.266 --> 00:39:44.022
It's not like this mission
is harder than the previous ones.

00:39:44.200 --> 00:39:45.550
We should try to persuade him.

00:39:47.480 --> 00:39:48.599
If we head inside again,

00:39:48.599 --> 00:39:51.000
someone will die
if he comes out with a cleaver.

00:39:51.000 --> 00:39:52.133
We should head back first.

00:39:52.280 --> 00:39:54.599
You'd never be so quick
to give up before.

00:39:56.000 --> 00:39:58.590
I'm not trying to give up here.
I just don't know what to do.

00:39:58.599 --> 00:39:59.880
But I know what to do.

00:39:59.880 --> 00:40:00.933
What should we do, then?

00:40:05.480 --> 00:40:06.400
I'm thinking about it.

00:40:07.280 --> 00:40:08.239
Right now?

00:40:11.559 --> 00:40:12.679
Who's there?

00:40:17.159 --> 00:40:18.039
It's you guys again.

00:40:18.244 --> 00:40:19.280
Our tavern isn't open yet.

00:40:19.280 --> 00:40:20.355
Please come again later.

00:40:20.679 --> 00:40:22.119
We're here to pay off his tab.

00:40:22.355 --> 00:40:23.133
Pay off his tab?

00:40:23.320 --> 00:40:24.800
We'll pay off

00:40:24.960 --> 00:40:26.440
all of Zhao Wanli's tab.

00:40:29.488 --> 00:40:32.070
I remember that you came here
to procure a painting from him.

00:40:32.480 --> 00:40:34.440
You two are quite sincere, aren't you?

00:40:35.044 --> 00:40:36.150
His tab has been paid off.

00:40:36.320 --> 00:40:37.480
I'll return the rest to you.

00:40:38.960 --> 00:40:39.519
By the way,

00:40:39.880 --> 00:40:41.840
has he ever mentioned

00:40:41.840 --> 00:40:43.079
that he had a painting

00:40:43.079 --> 00:40:45.599
called the Autumn Twilight Painting?

00:40:45.679 --> 00:40:46.559
A landscape painting?

00:40:47.159 --> 00:40:48.719
He does draw paintings all day long.

00:40:49.159 --> 00:40:50.480
But I don't know which one of them

00:40:50.490 --> 00:40:51.800
is the Autumn Twilight Painting.

00:40:51.920 --> 00:40:53.509
Why is he this despondent, then?

00:40:53.510 --> 00:40:55.111
Why does he spend his days drinking?

00:40:56.920 --> 00:40:58.000
You see,

00:40:59.639 --> 00:41:02.800
Zhao Wanli was
a man of talent and pride.

00:41:03.320 --> 00:41:05.920
In his youth, he was also
full of vigor and ambition.

00:41:05.933 --> 00:41:06.690
He even swore

00:41:06.700 --> 00:41:09.200
that he wouldn't get married
until he passed the imperial exam.

00:41:09.400 --> 00:41:10.719
But in the end,

00:41:11.079 --> 00:41:13.039
he failed the imperial exam
time and time again.

00:41:13.119 --> 00:41:14.840
That was how he ended up like this.

00:41:14.840 --> 00:41:15.639
So,

00:41:15.760 --> 00:41:18.119
he kept taking the imperial exam

00:41:18.155 --> 00:41:19.550
without seeking another path, huh?

00:41:19.559 --> 00:41:21.119
He's so darned stubborn.

00:41:21.190 --> 00:41:22.711
I tried to convince him to give up.

00:41:22.960 --> 00:41:24.559
But he said I didn't know him.

00:41:25.159 --> 00:41:26.360
I don't.

00:41:26.800 --> 00:41:28.639
But he doesn't know me either.

00:41:29.320 --> 00:41:30.400
That fool.

00:41:34.039 --> 00:41:35.599
After that, he said

00:41:35.719 --> 00:41:37.840
that fame and fortune
were but an illusion.

00:41:38.320 --> 00:41:39.280
In the end?

00:41:39.480 --> 00:41:41.177
He started drowning himself in sorrow.

00:41:41.200 --> 00:41:42.800
If I didn't sell any liquor to him,

00:41:42.810 --> 00:41:43.844
he would fall out with me.

00:41:43.866 --> 00:41:45.200
I couldn't do anything about him.

00:41:47.079 --> 00:41:49.119
Does he drink at your tavern every day?

00:41:49.519 --> 00:41:50.320
Yeah.

00:41:50.480 --> 00:41:51.480
Only our tavern

00:41:51.480 --> 00:41:53.480
allowed him to run up such a tab.

00:41:53.719 --> 00:41:54.519
Moreover,

00:41:54.519 --> 00:41:55.760
he's very picky.

00:41:56.239 --> 00:41:58.599
He only loves
the Nv'er Hong liquor we serve here.

00:42:05.199 --> 00:42:06.199
You're here again.

00:42:07.559 --> 00:42:08.559
Beautiful flowers.

00:42:08.559 --> 00:42:09.559
Zhao.

00:42:09.610 --> 00:42:11.230
- You're closing your stall, huh?
- Zhao.

00:42:11.239 --> 00:42:12.000
Yes.

00:42:12.039 --> 00:42:14.760
Let's drink today
while our liquor remains.

00:42:17.400 --> 00:42:18.599
Oh, my dear.

00:42:18.599 --> 00:42:19.639
Scholar Zhao.

00:42:45.540 --> 00:42:49.690
Flickering candles scatter shadows
by the window

00:42:50.140 --> 00:42:54.310
The bronze mirror catches
a wedding gown meant to be sent away

00:42:54.720 --> 00:42:59.050
Magnolias in bloom, a dream cut short

00:42:59.280 --> 00:43:03.200
One love, one daring play

00:43:03.620 --> 00:43:07.280
Someone covets you

00:43:08.380 --> 00:43:13.030
Someone dreams of taking you

00:43:13.030 --> 00:43:17.380
But my heart's never wavered

00:43:17.650 --> 00:43:25.120
In the gold-lit wreckage of daylight,
I gather our moments

00:43:26.600 --> 00:43:31.120
My breath lifts
the dust from your skin

00:43:31.480 --> 00:43:35.920
My gaze slips
into the cracks of your glaze

00:43:35.920 --> 00:43:40.540
My palm brushes the rust of your past

